    public class BaseActivity
extends androidx.appcompat.app.AppCompatActivity
implements com.google.android.material.navigation.NavigationView.OnNavigationItemSelectedListener, AddPaymentFragment.OnFragmentInteractionListener, com.google.android.gms.maps.OnMapReadyCallback, TaskLoadedCallback, com.google.android.gms.location.LocationListener
    this is a class of base activity, it contains google map api, side bar, notifications and so on Reference: https://www.tutorialspoint.com/how-to-show-current-location-on-a-google-map-on-android direction api example: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wRDLjUK8nyU, Created by Vishal on 10/20/2018.
